fields.title: Code 1
fields.description:
Applicants who applied for a learners licence Code 1 must answer:
1. Section B
2. Section C and
3. Section D

fields.title: Code 2 & 3
fields.description:
Applicants who applied for a learners licence Code 2 or 3 must answer:
1. Section B
2. Section C and
3. Section E
